⁣

🚭 Improving air quality and reducing tobacco use by expanding the number of smoke-free public spaces⁣
🚲 Promoting physical activity by building hundreds of miles of new bike lanes.⁣
🌳 Investing in green spaces and planning to plant 3 million trees by 2030.⁣
⁣
